ast Guard, from the coroner to suicide prevention advocates.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aSuicide victimszCaliforniazSan Francisco. 0aSuicidezCaliforniazSan Francisco. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aamerican bridges.  aamerican mysteries.  aamerican tragedy.  abridges and suicide.  acalifornia history.  acalifornia mysteries.  acalifornia travel guide.  acrime and mystery.  acrisis prevention.  adeath and dying.  afamous bridges.  ahuman stories.  amental health and suicide.  amental health in america.  amental health nonfiction.  apacific us travel.  apsychology and mental health.  apsychology and sociology.  apsychology of suicide.  asan francisco history.  asuicide and mental illness.  asuicide counseling.  asuicide prevention.  atragic stories.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052027240840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052095140240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520951402423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520951402/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY